description: If you’re lookin’ for a truck that serves high-quality burgers, made with the best local ingredients, including pasture-raised, antibiotic-free beef, then you’re definitely in luck because Wally & Buck is makin’ Missoula dreams come with their mouthwatering menu that matches this exact criteria. Be sure to bust out and try some of these amazing blazin’ burgers, like the Wally (quarter-pound patty with sharp Oregon cheddar, bacon jam, griddled onion, and more) or the Bean Town (Organic bean patty, seasonal herbs, and toppings galore). Whether you visit now or later, you’ll always be delighted by their delicious Rotator (the offering that changes weekly). These burgers leave foodies absolutely awestruck, so of course all of Missoula loves Wally & Buck, and so will you.
name: Wally & Buck
